Industrial AI-Powered Infrastructure
1. Executive Project Summary
The objective is to architect and deploy a sophisticated "Digital Twin" for an industrial environment,
specifically a hospital. This AI-managed infrastructure oversees procurement, sales, patient management,
and scheduling. By integrating a natural language interface with a live database, the system allows staff
to query real-time data with immediate, context-aware responses. 
2. Technical Architecture & Tech Stack
To ensure high performance and data integrity, the system utilizes a modern full-stack approach with
specialized AI integration. 
Layer Recommended
Technology Strategic Purpose
Frontend React.js / Tailwind CSS Fast, responsive dashboards for staff data entry.
Backend Node.js / Express Handling high-concurrency requests and API logic.
Database (Hard
Facts) PostgreSQL Transactional data: Inventory, Schedules,
Admissions.
