memory.
3. The "Brain": RAG & Text-to-SQL
The intelligence of the system relies on Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG). Unlike traditional AI,
this system does not "guess." When a user asks a question, the AI performs the following: 
Intent Recognition: Identifies if the user is asking for a count (SQL) or a summary (Vector Search).
Data Fetching: Pulls the exact record (e.g., John Smith's current ward) from the database.
Synthesis: Combines raw data with natural language for a clear, professional response.
